title: Dark Entities
subTitle: In 1977, the Winters siblings inherit a mysterious house holding dark secrets that threaten everything they hold dear. They exhaust logical explanations without success, forcing them to seek help from a parapsychologist as supernatural forces become life threatening.

title: Sapien
subTitle: After a sudden breakup with her boyfriend, popular influencer Abby Soulseeker sets out as a solo traveler documenting her journey for her fans. At first, the world seems like a new incredible place to explore, but she quickly realizes she has crossed the threshold of evil where a demon haunted world awaits bent on her destruction.

title: Spookt
subTitle: The secrets of a small town are revealed when an investigator and a skeptic join up to search for a missing girl and the infamous Dr. Byler.

title: Scare Zone
subTitle: A crazed killer unleashes bloody terror at a haunted-house attraction.

title: Country of Hotels
subTitle: At a decaying hotel, the desperate souls who pass through the room 508 experience strange effects.

title: Beyond the Chamber of Terror
subTitle: Nash Caruthers is on a deadly collision course with the people that tore his world apart.

subTitle: A couple struggling with infertility turns to a mysterious organization for help, only to realize that their baby may not be entirely human.
